.SS Autogrowing textarea example
Make a textarea autogrow while typing:
.SS JavaScript
.IP
.EX
function autoGrow(oField) {
  if (oField.scrollHeight > oField.clientHeight) {
    oField.style.height = \[ga]${oField.scrollHeight}px\[ga];
  }
}
.EE
